data.description: Introducing a custom built, original 1 owner home in the Northeast. This property has 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, a split-wing home, featuring a formal dining area, large open kitchen with island and breakfast nook that overlooks into the cozy living room with a fireplace. Through the indoor laundry room step into an oversized 3 car garage with lots of room for storage and a workbench. RV parking on the side! The backyard is a lush oasis that’s perfect for outdoor entertaining and relaxation. Complete with a covered patio, built-in BBQ, above ground spa and space in the back corner of the lot for a personal fruits and vegetable garden.
